"Set up a Bambu printer connection with OctoPrint-BambuConnector to enable "
"automatic configuration."
msgstr ""

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:45
msgid "Printer IP / hostname"
msgstr "Drucker-IP / Hostname"

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:51
msgid ""
"IP address of your Bambu Lab printer (P1/A1 series, LAN mode). The X1 series"
" is not supported."
msgstr ""
"IP-Adresse deines Bambu-Lab-Druckers (P1-/A1-Serie, LAN-Modus). Die X1-Serie"
" wird nicht unterstützt."

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:55
msgid "Access code"
msgstr "Zugangscode"

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:61
msgid "LAN access code, shown on the printer display under network settings."
msgstr ""
"LAN-Zugangscode, am Druckerdisplay unter den Netzwerkeinstellungen "
"angezeigt."

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:67
msgid "Test connection"
msgstr "Verbindung testen"

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:70
msgid "Connection successful!"
msgstr "Verbindung erfolgreich!"

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:72
msgid "Printer rejected the access code."
msgstr "Drucker hat den Zugangscode abgelehnt."

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:74
msgid "Printer is unreachable."
msgstr "Drucker ist nicht erreichbar."

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:75
msgid "Connection timed out."
msgstr "Zeitüberschreitung bei der Verbindung."

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:76
msgid "Connection failed."
msgstr "Verbindung fehlgeschlagen."

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:79
msgid "Stream server"
msgstr "Stream-Server"

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:81
msgid "HTTP port"
msgstr "HTTP-Port"

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:88
msgid "Port of the local MJPEG server started by this plugin."
msgstr "Port des lokalen MJPEG-Servers, der von diesem Plugin gestartet wird."

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:92
msgid "Bind address"
msgstr "Bind-Adresse"

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:96
msgid "this machine only, safe"
msgstr "nur dieser Rechner, sicher"

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:98
msgid "whole network"
msgstr "gesamtes Netzwerk"

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:103
msgid ""
"The stream server has no authentication. With 0.0.0.0 anyone on your network"
" can watch the camera. Required for the live view in the browser unless you "
"set a stream URL override below."
msgstr ""
"Der Stream-Server hat keine Authentifizierung. Mit 0.0.0.0 kann jeder in "
"deinem Netzwerk die Kamera sehen. Für die Live-Ansicht im Browser "
"erforderlich, sofern du unten keine abweichende Stream-URL angibst."

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:105
msgid ""
"With 127.0.0.1 snapshots and timelapse work, but the browser live view does "
"not (unless you use a reverse proxy and a stream URL override)."
msgstr ""
"Mit 127.0.0.1 funktionieren Schnappschüsse und Zeitraffer, die Live-Ansicht "
"im Browser jedoch nicht (es sei denn, du verwendest einen Reverse-Proxy und "
"eine abweichende Stream-URL)."

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:114
msgid "Copy snapshot URL"
msgstr "Schnappschuss-URL kopieren"

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:127
msgid "Copy stream URL"
msgstr "Stream-URL kopieren"

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:135
msgid "Stream URL override"
msgstr "Abweichende Stream-URL"

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:141
msgid ""
"Optional. Use this if the stream is served through a reverse proxy. Leave "
"empty to use the port above directly."
msgstr ""
"Optional. Verwende dies, wenn der Stream über einen Reverse-Proxy "
"bereitgestellt wird. Leer lassen, um den Port oben direkt zu verwenden."

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:144
#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_tab.jinja2:95
#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_tab.jinja2:172
msgid "Status"
msgstr "Status"

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:148
msgid "Running"
msgstr "Läuft"

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:149
msgid "Stopped"
msgstr "Gestoppt"

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:153
msgid "viewer(s)"
msgstr "Zuschauer"

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:159
msgid "Restart stream server"
msgstr "Stream-Server neu starten"

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:167
msgid "Resolution"
msgstr "Auflösung"

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:173
msgid "Override resolution"
msgstr "Auflösung überschreiben"

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:175
msgid ""
"Off by default: the printer dictates the frame size. Only enable this if you"
" specifically need to force a width/height — a value that does not match the"
" printer's stream can corrupt the image."
msgstr ""
"Standardmäßig aus: Der Drucker gibt die Bildgröße vor. Nur aktivieren, wenn "
"du Breite/Höhe wirklich erzwingen musst — ein Wert, der nicht zum Stream des"
" Druckers passt, kann das Bild beschädigen."

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:179
msgid "Width"
msgstr "Breite"

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:185
#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:195
msgid "Only used when 'Override resolution' is enabled."
msgstr "Wird nur verwendet, wenn „Auflösung überschreiben“ aktiviert ist."

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:189
msgid "Height"
msgstr "Höhe"

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:200
msgid "Rotation (degrees)"
msgstr "Drehung (Grad)"

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:207
msgid "1-359 degrees, -1 disables rotation."
msgstr "1-359 Grad, -1 deaktiviert die Drehung."

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:211
msgid "Capture pause (seconds)"
msgstr "Aufnahmepause (Sekunden)"

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:218
msgid "Pause between captured frames (--encodewait). Default 0.5."
msgstr "Pause zwischen aufgenommenen Bildern (--encodewait). Standard 0.5."

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:226
msgid "Show activity dot (red dot every other frame)"
msgstr "Aktivitätspunkt anzeigen (roter Punkt bei jedem zweiten Bild)"

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:231
msgid "Show FPS watermark (costs CPU)"
msgstr "FPS-Wasserzeichen anzeigen (kostet CPU)"

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:238
msgid "Timelapse downloads"
msgstr "Zeitraffer-Downloads"

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:240
msgid "Filename suffix"
msgstr "Dateinamen-Suffix"

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:245
msgid ""
"Optional. Appended to each downloaded timelapse filename before the "
"extension (e.g. _bambu) so they're easy to tell apart from OctoPrint's own "
"renders."
msgstr ""
"Optional. Wird an jeden heruntergeladenen Zeitraffer-Dateinamen vor der "
"Endung angehängt (z. B. _bambu), damit du sie leicht von OctoPrints eigenen "
"Renderings unterscheiden kannst."

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:253
msgid "Convert downloaded .avi to .mp4"
msgstr "Heruntergeladene .avi in .mp4 umwandeln"

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:255
msgid ""
"Re-encodes each copied .avi to .mp4 (removing the .avi) using OctoPrint's "
"ffmpeg. Skipped while printing."
msgstr ""
"Wandelt jede kopierte .avi mit OctoPrints ffmpeg in .mp4 um (und entfernt "
"die .avi). Während des Drucks übersprungen."

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:259
msgid "ffmpeg found"
msgstr ""

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:264
msgid ""
"ffmpeg not found — set it under Settings → Webcam &amp; Timelapse. "
"Conversion will be skipped until then."
msgstr ""

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:267
msgid "Checking ffmpeg…"
msgstr ""

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:277
msgid "Automatically pull new timelapses after a print"
msgstr ""

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:279
msgid ""
"After a print finishes, copy/move the printer's new timelapse automatically "
"— but only once the printer is idle and OctoPrint has finished rendering its"
" own timelapse."
msgstr ""

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:284
msgid "Auto-pull action"
msgstr ""

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:287
msgid "Copy (keep on SD card)"
msgstr ""

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:288
msgid "Move (delete from SD card)"
msgstr ""

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:294
msgid "Delay after print"
msgstr ""

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:302
msgid "seconds"
msgstr ""

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:304
msgid ""
"How long to wait after a print before checking the SD card (the printer "
"writes its timelapse with a delay)."
msgstr ""

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:310
msgid "Daemon"
msgstr "Daemon"

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:316
msgid "Automatically restart the stream server after crashes"
msgstr "Stream-Server nach Abstürzen automatisch neu starten"

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:321
msgid "Log HTTP requests of the stream server (debug)"
msgstr "HTTP-Anfragen des Stream-Servers protokollieren (Debug)"

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:326
msgid "Max restarts"
msgstr "Maximale Neustarts"

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:332
msgid ""
"Give up auto-restarting after this many crashes within the restart window. "
"Only used when auto-restart is enabled."
msgstr ""
"Bricht den automatischen Neustart ab, nachdem so viele Abstürze innerhalb "
"des Neustart-Zeitfensters aufgetreten sind. Wird nur verwendet, wenn der "
"automatische Neustart aktiviert ist."

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:336
msgid "Restart window (seconds)"
msgstr "Neustart-Zeitfenster (Sekunden)"

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:342
msgid ""
"Time window over which the crash count is measured. Only used when auto-"
"restart is enabled."
msgstr ""
"Zeitfenster, über das die Anzahl der Abstürze gemessen wird. Wird nur "
"verwendet, wenn der automatische Neustart aktiviert ist."

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:345
msgid "Diagnostics"
msgstr "Diagnose"

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:351
msgid "Query stream server (/?info)"
msgstr "Stream-Server abfragen (/?info)"

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:355
msgid ""
"Fetches live stats from the local stream server (the access code is never "
"returned). The server must be running."
msgstr ""
"Ruft Live-Statistiken vom lokalen Stream-Server ab (der Zugangscode wird nie"
" zurückgegeben). Der Server muss laufen."

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:366
msgid "Powered by"
msgstr "Bereitgestellt durch"

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_settings.jinja2:369
msgid "by Igor Maculan, Christopher RYU, Shell Shrader and disconn3ct."
msgstr "von Igor Maculan, Christopher RYU, Shell Shrader und disconn3ct."

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_tab.jinja2:2
msgid "BambuCam Timelapse"
msgstr "BambuCam Zeitraffer"

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_tab.jinja2:4
msgid ""
"List, copy, move and delete the timelapse videos stored on the Bambu "
"printer's SD card. Copied videos appear in OctoPrint's Timelapse tab."
msgstr ""
"Liste, kopiere, verschiebe und lösche die Zeitraffer-Videos, die auf der SD-"
"Karte des Bambu-Druckers gespeichert sind. Kopierte Videos erscheinen im "
"Zeitraffer-Tab von OctoPrint."

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_tab.jinja2:11
msgid "Refresh list"
msgstr "Liste aktualisieren"

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_tab.jinja2:17
msgid "Copy"
msgstr "Kopieren"

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_tab.jinja2:21
msgid "Move"
msgstr "Verschieben"

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_tab.jinja2:25
msgid "Delete"
msgstr "Löschen"

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_tab.jinja2:33
msgid "Sort"
msgstr ""

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_tab.jinja2:40
msgid "Sort by name (descending)"
msgstr ""

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_tab.jinja2:46
msgid "Sort by date (descending)"
msgstr ""

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_tab.jinja2:52
msgid "Sort by file size (descending)"
msgstr ""

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_tab.jinja2:60
msgid "Move and delete are disabled while a print is running."
msgstr ""
"Verschieben und Löschen sind während eines laufenden Drucks deaktiviert."

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_tab.jinja2:65
msgid "Login failed — check the access code in Settings > BambuCam."
msgstr ""
"Anmeldung fehlgeschlagen — prüfe den Zugangscode unter Einstellungen > "
"BambuCam."

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_tab.jinja2:69
msgid "Printer not reachable. Is it powered on and on the network?"
msgstr "Drucker nicht erreichbar. Ist er eingeschaltet und im Netzwerk?"

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_tab.jinja2:72
msgid "The printer did not respond in time. Try again."
msgstr "Der Drucker hat nicht rechtzeitig geantwortet. Versuche es erneut."

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_tab.jinja2:76
msgid "Could not list the timelapses. Check the connection and try again."
msgstr ""
"Die Zeitraffer konnten nicht aufgelistet werden. Prüfe die Verbindung und "
"versuche es erneut."

#: octoprint_bambucam/templates/bambucam_tab.jinja2:80
msgid ""
"No timelapses found. Insert an SD card and enable timelapse capture in the "
"slicer/printer."
msgstr ""
"Keine Zeitraffer gefunden. Lege eine SD-Karte ein und aktiviere die "
